#: index.docbook:64
msgid "The <application>ht://dig</application> Programs"
msgstr "Os Programas do <application>ht://dig</application>"

#: index.docbook:66
msgid ""
"There are three programs KDE needs that come with "
"<application>ht://dig</application>: <command>htdig</command>, "
"<command>htsearch</command> and <command>htmerge</command>"
". For each program you have to provide the full path including the program "
"name, for example: <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/bin/htdig</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Existem três programas que o KDE necessita que vêm com o "
"<application>ht://dig</application>: o <command>htdig</command>, o "
"<command>htsearch</command> e o <command>htmerge</command>. Para cada "
"programa, tens de indicar a localização completa, incluindo o nome do "
"programa, por exemplo: <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/bin/htdig</filename>."

#: index.docbook:72
msgid ""
"Where exactly these programs are installed depends on your operating system "
"or your distribution. However, there are some good guesses you might want to "
"try:"
msgstr ""
"A localização exacta destes programas depende do teu sistema operativo ou "
"distribuição. Contudo, existem alguns bons palpites que podes tentar:"

#: index.docbook:76
msgid ""
"<command>htdig</command> and <command>htmerge</command> are often found in "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/bin/</filename> or in something like "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/local/www/htdig/bin/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"o <command>htdig</command> e o <command>htmerge</command>"
" estão normalmente na  <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/bin/</filename> "
"ou em algo como <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/local/www/htdig/bin/</filename>."

#: index.docbook:76
msgid ""
"the <command>htsearch</command> command is often found in a sub directory "
"called <filename class=\"directory\">cgi-bin</filename>, for example "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/local/httpd/cgi-bin/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"o comando <command>htsearch</command> está normalmente numa sub-directoria "
"chamada <filename class=\"directory\">cgi-bin</filename>, como por exemplo "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/local/httpd/cgi-bin/</filename>."

#: index.docbook:90
msgid ""
"To find out where for example <command>htdig</command> is installed you can "
"always type <command>whereis htdig</command> on the console. "
"<command>whereis</command> will look for the specified command in the "
"standard execution path directories. However, directories like <filename "
"class=\"directory\">cgi-bin</filename> are often not in the standard "
"execution path."
msgstr ""
"Para descobrires onde, por exemplo, o programa <command>htdig</command> "
"está instalado podes sempre escrever na consola <command>whereis "
"htdig</command>. O <command>whereis</command> irá procurar pelo comando "
"especificado nas directorias de execução normais. Porém, as directorias "
"como a <filename class=\"directory\">cgi-bin</filename> não estão "
"normalmente numa directoria de execução."

#: index.docbook:100
msgid "Scope and Search Paths"
msgstr "Âmbito e Locais de Pesquisa"

#: index.docbook:102
msgid ""
"In this section you can choose which help resources should be indexed, "
"<abbrev>i.e.</abbrev> made available to the search engine."
msgstr ""
"Nesta secção podes escolher que recursos de ajuda devem ser indexados, "
"<abbrev>i.e.</abbrev>, tornados disponíveis ao motor de busca."

#: index.docbook:105
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Scope</guilabel> frame you can select some typical "
"resources you want to be indexed, <abbrev>i.e.</abbrev> the KDE help files, "
"and the information offered by the <command>man</command> and "
"<command>info</command> commands. Note that some of those may still be "
"disabled, which means that support for them has not been added yet."
msgstr ""
"Na área <guilabel>Âmbito</guilabel> podes seleccionar alguns recursos "
"típicos que queiras indexar, <abbrev>i.e.</abbrev>"
" os ficheiros de ajuda do KDE e a informação dos comandos "
"<command>man</command> e <command>info</command>. Repara que alguns destes "
"podem ainda estar desactivados, o que significa que o suporte para eles "
"ainda não foi adicionado."

#: index.docbook:111
msgid ""
"Maybe you have additional files you want to access using the KDE Help "
"Center's fulltext search feature. For example, you might have an "
"<abbrev>HTML</abbrev> reference installed in "
"<filename>/home/jdoe/docs/selfhtml</filename>. By adding this path to the "
"list of additional search paths you make this documentation available to KDE "
"Help Center's fulltext search, too. Just click on the "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> button and a file dialog will ask you for an "
"additional search directory. Select "
"<filename>/home/jdoe/docs/selfhtml</filename> and click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>. To remove an additional search path, just select "
"it and click <guibutton>Delete</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Talvez tenhas ficheiros adicionais aos quais queiras aceder utilizando a "
"pesquisa de texto do Centro de Ajuda do KDE. Por exemplo, podes ter uma "
"referência em <abbrev>HTML</abbrev> instalada em "
"<filename>/home/jdoe/docs/selfhtml</filename>. Ao adicionares esta "
"localização à lista de directorias de pesquisa, passas a disponibilizar "
"também esta documentação na pesquisa do Centro de Ajuda. Basta carregares "
"no botão <guibutton>Adicionar</guibutton> e uma janela de ficheiros "
"pedir-te-á uma nova directoria de pesquisa. Selecciona "
"<filename>/home/jdoe/docs/selfhtml</filename> e carrega em "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>. Para removeres uma directoria de pesquisa, basta "
"seleccioná-la e carregares em <guibutton>Apagar</guibutton>."

#: index.docbook:122
msgid ""
"Your changes to the scope and additional search paths will not take effect "
"if you don't click on the <guibutton>Generate index ...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"As tuas modificações no âmbito e nas directorias de pesquisa não "
"tomarão efeito se não carregares no botão <guibutton>Gerar "
"índice...</guibutton>."

#: index.docbook:129
msgid "Selecting the language"
msgstr "Seleccionar a língua"

#: index.docbook:130
msgid ""
"You can select the language you want the help files in using the combo box "
"labeled <guilabel>Language Settings</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Podes seleccionar a língua na qual desejas os ficheiros de ajuda através "
"da opção <guilabel>Configuração da Língua</guilabel>"

